&lt;p&gt;Anyone who knows me will tell you that I'm pretty foolhardy and don't usually keep out of potentially dangerous situations. Well, I stepped on a quarter sized glob of tar and I'm still carrying part of it around with me. It won't come off.&lt;/p&gt;

