&lt;p&gt;When pelicans want to dry their wings out they hold them like this.  When they get oil on them they attempt to dry them as well except of course the oil won't dry out.  I couldn't get close enough to see if this bird was oiled but given the amount of time he spent holding his wings out I believe he was&lt;/p&gt;

